						<h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-2xl font-normal mb-6" style="font-family: 'Merriweather', serif; color: #666;">
							Your first step into speaking Colloquial Tibetan
						</h2>

						<p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6 font-semibold" style="font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; color: #000; font-size: 16pt;">
